                    <note>Fiey provides the following bibliographic citations: <quote source="#bib1227-1">E. Honigmann, "Stephen of Ephesus ( 448) and the Legend of the Seven Sleepers",
dans sa Patristic Studies (Citta del Vaticano, 1953 : SeT 173), 125- 68 (ch. XVII).
Y. Moubarac, etude d'apres les Opera Minora deL. Massignon (Beyrouth, 1963),
III, 104- 80.
